<emphasis bold="true" box="[813,1111,1496,1521]" pageId="5" pageNumber="50">Distribution and ecology.</emphasis>
<collectingCountry box="[1123,1190,1497,1521]" name="Brazil" pageId="5" pageNumber="50">Brazil</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[1251,1355,1497,1521]" name="Colombia" pageId="5" pageNumber="50">Colombia</collectingCountry>
(Lisboa 1976; 
<bibRefCitation author="Gradstein SR &amp; Costa DP" box="[923,1207,1531,1555]" pageId="5" pageNumber="50" pagination="1 - 336" refId="ref8589" refString="Gradstein SR, Costa DP (2003) Hepaticae and anthocerotae of Brazil. Memoirs of the New York Botanical Garden 87: 1 - 336." type="journal article" year="2003">Gradstein and Costa 2003</bibRefCitation>
; Pinzón et al. 2003; 
<bibRefCitation author="Carmo DM &amp; Peralta DF" box="[813,1074,1565,1589]" pageId="5" pageNumber="50" pagination="254 - 265" refId="ref8027" refString="Carmo DM, Peralta DF (2016) Survey of bryophytes in Serra da Canastra National Park, Minas Gerais, Brazil. Acta Botanica Brasilica 30 (2): 254 - 265. https: // doi. org / 10.1590 / 0102 - 33062015 abb 0235" type="journal article" year="2016">Carmo and Peralta 2016</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Costa DP &amp; Peralta DF &amp; Buck WR &amp; Larrain J &amp; Von Konrat M" box="[1085,1267,1565,1589]" pageId="5" pageNumber="50" pagination="201 - 217" refId="ref8211" refString="Costa DP, Peralta DF, Buck WR, Larrain J, Von Konrat M (2017) Serra do Curicuriari, Amazonas, Brasil: a primeira analise briofloris- tica de uma montanha brasileira na floresta amazonica. Phytotaxa 303 (3): 201 - 217. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / phytotaxa. 303.3.1" type="journal article" year="2017">Costa et al. 2017</bibRefCitation>
). Brazilian biomes and states: Amazonia (Amazonas and Roraima) and Atlantic Forest (Minas Gerais) (
<bibRefCitation author="Carmo DM &amp; Peralta DF" pageId="5" pageNumber="50" pagination="254 - 265" refId="ref8027" refString="Carmo DM, Peralta DF (2016) Survey of bryophytes in Serra da Canastra National Park, Minas Gerais, Brazil. Acta Botanica Brasilica 30 (2): 254 - 265. https: // doi. org / 10.1590 / 0102 - 33062015 abb 0235" type="journal article" year="2016">Carmo and Peralta 2016</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Costa DP &amp; Peralta DF &amp; Buck WR &amp; Larrain J &amp; Von Konrat M" box="[877,1062,1667,1691]" pageId="5" pageNumber="50" pagination="201 - 217" refId="ref8211" refString="Costa DP, Peralta DF, Buck WR, Larrain J, Von Konrat M (2017) Serra do Curicuriari, Amazonas, Brasil: a primeira analise briofloris- tica de uma montanha brasileira na floresta amazonica. Phytotaxa 303 (3): 201 - 217. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / phytotaxa. 303.3.1" type="journal article" year="2017">Costa et al. 2017</bibRefCitation>
); and Brazilian Cerrado (Maranhão; new data). We collected this species near an open, sunny, sandy stream bank.
</paragraph>
